name: p_astro
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "p_astro" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 810bd5413ba1bce5153a2ab2616a94530dceaa34b14699aa794702a12ecdad04
  patches:
    # simplify requirements for conda-forge
    - requirements.patch
    # update namespace package declaration
    - namespace-package.patch

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  entry_points:
    - p_astro_compute_means = ligo.p_astro_utils:compute_counts_mean
    - p_astro_histogram_by_bin = ligo.p_astro_utils:histogram_by_bin

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.7
    - setuptools
  run:
    - astropy
    - h5py
    - numpy
    # no py310, see https://git.ligo.org/lscsoft/p-astro/-/issues/18
    - python >=3.7,<3.10a0
    - python-lal
    - python-lalinspiral
    - python-lalsimulation
    - python-ligo-lw
    - scipy

test:
  requires:
    - pip
    - pytest
  commands:
    # check dependencies
    - python -m pip check
    # run test suite
    - python -m pytest --pyargs -ra -v ligo.tests
    # check scripts
    - p_astro_compute_means --help
    - p_astro_histogram_by_bin --help

about:
  home: https://lscsoft.docs.ligo.org/p-astro/
  dev_url: https://git.ligo.org/lscsoft/p-astro.git
  doc_url: https://lscsoft.docs.ligo.org/p-astro/
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Low-latency estimation of category-wise astrophysical probability of GW candidates

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - duncanmmacleod
